oriel
-----

a very simple and customizable javascript slideshow player.

better documentation forthcoming, but see:
http://mjhoy.github.com/oriel/


Generating Documentation
------------------------

I use `docco` to generate a nice HTML document from the source.

To (re)generate, run:

$ docco src/*.js src/plugins/*.js

In addition, there is HTML documentation/examples in the `doc` directory.
Currently changes to `src` must be copied over to `doc`. (Todo: a better system
that works with GH pages.)

To copy, run:

$ cp src/*.js src/plugins/*.js docs

